; Exercise 32. 
; Design the function image-area, which counts the number of pixels in a given
; image.

; Image -> Number
; return the number of pixels in the given image
; given:  (rectangle 10 20 "solid" "red")
; expect: 200
(define (image-area img) (* (image-width img) (image-height img)))
